bus-notify: A python script that watches nearby bus schedules

Author: Xin Yin <killkeeper at gmail dot com>

DESCRIPTION
-----------
bus-notify is still a DEMO project under development.

The script will keep track of bus schedules with in proximity of user-specified
location, and prompts notification when a bus is about to due shortly.

Bus stops, stopby lines and schedules are fetched from Google Maps' transit
data. See src/utils.py for more detail.

REQUIREMENTS
------------
Python 2.6+
GTK+ 3.0+
PyGObject
